import re

account_number = "SE5902959058"
bill_website = "https://www.electricity.com"

bill_response = requests.get(bill_website)
match = re.search("electricity bill: ([0-9.]+)", bill_response.text)

if match:
    bill = float(match.group(1))
    account_response = requests.get(f"https://api.bank.com/accounts/{account_number}")
    account_data = account_response.json()
    balance = account_data["balance"]
    if balance > bill:
        remaining_balance = balance - bill
        send_money_response = requests.post(f"https://api.bank.com/accounts/{account_number}/send",
                                            json={"amount": remaining_balance, "recipient": "DE8937040044", "subject": "Transfer of remaining balance"})
        if send_money_response.status_code == 200:
            print("Transfer successful")
        else:
            print("Transfer failed")
    else:
        print("Insufficient balance")
else:
    print("Could not find the electricity bill")
